      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i'm looking at houses in austin and i'm a bit confused about the earnest money part. like why is it being held in an escrow account instead of just going to the seller? and what happens if the inspection comes back with major issues?",
      "source": "evaluator",
      "targeted_response_start": "",
